{"tid":10901,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"你班emoji撚通通同我入嚟！！！","createTime":"2016-11-29T06:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T17:05:20.000Z","uid":3974,"like":27,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e088707985c74c75fc7dc4715089019c51745a","tid":10901,"uid":3974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFC56eL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFC56eL.jpg&h=8174a219&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你班柒頭反乜撚野emoji？<br />\n你當呢度邊撚度？<br />\n你反還反，admin又唔係唔理鳩你<br />\n你下下屌鳩其他user用emoji做乜撚？<br />\n明撚明emoji係LIHKG特色其一<br />\n個app description 都有寫<br />\n反乜撚？屌乜撚？玩分化？<br />\n定你地當呢度高登？<br />\nLIHKG唔可以有新氣象 新文化？<br />\n你班老屎忽渣撚哂骰咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/29/140551_8a752b1452a97ff8aa86b4f593535a07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F29%2F140551_8a752b1452a97ff8aa86b4f593535a07.jpg&h=06a56dac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你地唔係搞分化，就理性少少啦屌 <br />\n本來和和氣氣，比你班反emoji屌到個個面紅耳赤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：我唔撚用既 睇唔過眼姐<br />\n<br />\nBtw 🖕🏻"},{"pid":"b177cfd43cd9cf8ed85be5ecd9ac1e86f9da38aa","tid":10901,"uid":3974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:14:41.000Z","msg":"😴"},{"pid":"5c9ae3b6a5389d1a1a149545cbb989a49cf3b0da","tid":10901,"uid":4725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:15:32.000Z","msg":"認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2039bc7de9bfaf33153f31b3090e8b90e8edff88","tid":10901,"uid":3974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T06:16:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/